---
/**
 * Free Labeling 섹션 (무료 라벨링 체험)
 * @TASK P2-S1-T4
 * @SPEC docs/planning/06-screens.md#1.5-무료-라벨링-섹션
 *
 * 기능:
 * - 배경: bg-white
 * - 섹션 헤더: "무료 라벨링 체험"
 * - 설명 텍스트
 * - CTA: [무료 라벨링 체험하기] → /label 이동
 */
---

<section id="free-labeling" class="py-20 md:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-16 overflow-hidden relative">
      <!-- Background Pattern -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 tech-pattern opacity-20"></div>

      <!-- Blur Effects -->
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-48 h-48 bg-indigo-500/20 rounded-full blur-[80px]"></div>

      <div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Content -->
        <div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-full mb-6">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-400 text-sm">auto_awesome</span>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-300 uppercase tracking-wider">Free Service</span>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            무료 라벨링 체험
          </h2>

          <p class="text-lg text-white/80 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            원재료와 영양정보를 입력하면 EU/미국 규정에 맞는<br class="hidden md:block" />
            <strong class="text-white">라벨 초안을 무료로 생성</strong>해드립니다
          </p>

          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white/70">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-400 text-lg">check_circle</span>
              <span>EU FIC 규정 자동 준수</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white/70">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-400 text-lg">check_circle</span>
              <span>14대 알러젠 자동 감지</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white/70">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-400 text-lg">check_circle</span>
              <span>나트륨→소금, kcal→kJ 자동 변환</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white/70">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-400 text-lg">check_circle</span>
              <span>규정 준수율 체크리스트 제공</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <a
            href="/label"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-white text-navy rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-105 transition-all"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">science</span>
            무료 라벨링 체험하기
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Preview Card -->
        <div class="hidden lg:block">
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 pb-4 border-b border-white/10">
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-400"></div>
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400"></div>
              <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-400"></div>
              <span class="ml-auto text-xs text-white/50">Global Label AI</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Mock Label Output -->
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-white/70 space-y-2">
              <div class="text-blue-300">// EU Label Output</div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-400">INGREDIENTS:</span>
                <span class="text-white"> Water, <strong class="text-yellow-300">WHEAT</strong> flour,</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-white">Sugar, Salt, <strong class="text-yellow-300">SOY</strong> sauce</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-4">
                <span class="text-slate-400">NUTRITION (per 100g):</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-white">Energy: 350 kcal / 1464 kJ</div>
              <div class="text-white">Salt: 1.25g</div>
              <div class="mt-4 text-green-400">✓ FIC Article 18 Compliant</div>
              <div class="text-green-400">✓ Allergens Highlighted</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
